{{Infobox video game | image = | caption = | developer = Andromeda Software | publisher = [[Creative Sparks]] | designer = Pál Balog<ref name="giantlist">{{cite web |last1=Hague |first1=James |title=The Giant List of Classic Game Programmers |url=http://dadgum.com/giantlist/}}</ref> | composer = Zoltán Mericske | platforms = [[Commodore 64]] | released = 1984 | genre = [[Action game]] | modes = [[Single-player video game|Single-player]] }}
'''''Bird Mother''''' is an [[action game]] developed by Novotrade (Andromeda Software) and published by [[Creative Sparks]] for the [[Commodore 64]] in 1984. It was not ported to other systems.
==Gameplay== {{empty section|date=November 2015}}
==Reception== {{expand section|date=November 2015}}
''Bird Mother'' received review scores of 26/40 from ''[[Personal Computer Games]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/stream/personalcomputergames-magazine-14/PersonalComputerGames_14#page/n59/mode/2up/ |title=Personal Computer Games Magazine Issue 14 |publisher=Archive.org |date= |accessdate=2015-11-03}}</ref> and 33/40 from ''[[Computer & Video Games]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/stream/computer-video-games-magazine-037/CVG037_Nov_1984#page/n90/mode/1up/s |title=Computer and Video Games Magazine Issue 037 |publisher=Archive.org |date= |accessdate=2015-11-03}}</ref>
